<h3><b><i>&ldquo;</i></b><span style="font-weight: 400;">The best work, the best career, for you, the one that makes you happiest and most fulfilled, is going to be one that uses: your favorite transferable skills, in your favorite subjects, fields , or special knowledge, in a job that offers you your preferred people-environments, your preferred working conditions, with your preferred salary or other rewards, working toward your preferred goals and values.&rdquo;&nbsp;</span></h3>
<h3><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; Richard N. Bolles, What Color is Your Parachute?</span></h3>
